Text: In west sumatra there is a village names Muaro Labuh,haved 1000 a Big House
  you can call Rumah Gadang.So this is  unic and verry natural ,those The Big House
  exist until now from Dinasty age,and people around the 1000 big house also keep
  it from who people will change the cultural,and keep from change of the world.So
  this palace verry natural,you can so amazing looked this because this place verry
  traditional and original.But the people around this place knowing technologi,if
  you visit the place not to worry.In west sumatra ,in part of the village you can
  looked a big house,but in muaro labuah the only one place in village there 1000
  big house,from Internasional Minangkabau Airport to Muaro Labuah Village only 5
  hour,you can going with mini bus,during the journey you can find a beutifull lake
  in solok and beutifull marapi mountain,and natural view minang kabau.This is a cheap
  trip,but you can get expensive journey.This is one of the most place in the west
  sumatra,you can find it in google or other refrence.
